#. type: Content of: <div><h2>
msgid "The Education System in India"
msgstr "Hindistan'daki Eğitim Sistemi"

#. type: Content of: <div><address>
msgid ""
"by Dr. V. Sasi Kumar&#8239;<a href=\"#sasi\" id=\"sasi-rev\"><sup>[*]</sup></"
"a>"
